data.description: Welcome to this spacious 4 bedroom home with a full finished basement nestled in the quiet neighborhood of Hills Park on the vibrant Upper Westside of Atlanta. This residence offers a perfect blend of modern updates and classic charm, making it an ideal retreat in the heart of the city. Step inside to discover updates  throughout the home, including refinished hardwoods on the main level and fresh paint that brightens every corner, including the white kitchen cabinets. New light fixtures illuminate the space, highlighting the contemporary feel of the interior. The kitchen boasts all new appliances, including a new dishwasher, range, hood vent, and a forthcoming refrigerator installation, ensuring a seamless culinary experience for the new owners. The fully updated guest bathroom on the upper level exudes style and functionality. Outside, a large back deck provides a serene spot to relax and entertain, overlooking one of the largest backyards in the neighborhood, offering ample space for outdoor activities and gatherings.The finished basement presents versatile opportunities, whether utilized as an in-law suite, bonus room, media room, gym, or office, catering to the diverse needs of the homeowners. Additionally, a custom-ordered tornado shelter tucked away in the basement adds an extra layer of safety and peace of mind. Situated in a prime location, this home offers convenience with close proximity to Buckhead, Midtown Atlanta, Smyrna, and many other popular destinations, ensuring easy access to a myriad of dining, shopping, and entertainment options.  Don't miss the chance to make this remarkable property your new home sweet home!
